      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WOODCLIFF KABOOM (2) racing well without winning, placing at his last four runs. Last start finished 3rd on April 18 over 400m at this track behind Jacktavern Taz beaten 5 lengths (24.75) in an A8. Likely to be in the finish again. TEA LEAF THOR (6) flew the lids from trap five with a sensational turn of foot last time, going on to clock 24.65 when a 1.3 lengths winner over 400m at this track. Must be included in calculations. FALSE TEARS (5) is yet to find winning form this campaign but will appreciate the drop in grade. Unplaced first up at this track then improved into the minors last time, beaten 3.5 lengths, in an A7 at this track over 400m (24.73). Strong chance this easier company. UNDERGROUND SYD (4) was in the money last start here at this trip - likely to feature again.",
